let data
let i = 1
let dias = []

let dataInicial = $now.minus(86400000)
dataInicial = dataInicial.year + '-' + (dataInicial.month <= 9 ? '0' + dataInicial.month : dataInicial.month) + '-' + (dataInicial.day <= 9 ? '0' + dataInicial.day : dataInicial.day)

//dataInicial = '2025-10-22'

while (data != dataInicial && i <= 1000) {
    data = $now.minus(86400000 * i)
    data = data.year + '-' + (data.month <= 9 ? '0' + data.month : data.month) + '-' + (data.day <= 9 ? '0' + data.day : data.day)
    dias[dias.length] = data
    i++
}

dias = dias.reverse()

$input.item.json.data = dias

return $input.item
